KitKat::

She took a few steps forward. "Commander, when do we attack the 
enemy? I wish to do battle. I want to crush those bots into the 
ground and watch thier scrap corpses rust into oblivion."  She 
growled at the thought. "Yes Commander, When do we fight?"
